    <h1>Hi there!</h1>

    <p>I&rsquo;m an associate professor in the 
<a href="http://engineering.uci.edu/dept/eecs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Department of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a> at UC Irvine. My research is at the intersection of scientific machine learning and high-performance computing. I lead the 
