<a href="http://www.gatech.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Georgia Tech</a> in 2013 in the 
<a href="http://hpcgarage.org/wp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HPC Garage</a>. Prior to joining UCI, I was a research scientist at 
